									<span
										class="flex w-16 h-16 mx-auto items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold rounded-full bg-primary-50 text-primary-600"
									>
										1</span
									>
								</div>
								<div class="px-4">
									<h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold font-heading">Sovereignty</h3>
									<p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
										No surprise bills. Replace cloud lock-in with open-source tools that run on your hardware, on your own terms.
									</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="flex md:-mx-4">
								<div class="pr-4 sm:pl-4">
									<span
										class="flex w-16 h-16 mx-auto items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold rounded-full bg-primary-50 text-primary-600"
									>
										2</span
									>
								</div>
								<div class="px-4">
									<h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold font-heading">Mobility</h3>
									<p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
										Work anywhere, offline or online. Your environment stays consistent across devices, with sync only when you decide.
									</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="flex md:-mx-4">
								<div class="pr-4 sm:pl-4">
									<span
										class="flex w-16 h-16 mx-auto items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold rounded-full bg-primary-50 text-primary-600"
									>
										3</span
									>
								</div>
								<div class="px-4">
									<h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold font-heading">Resilience</h3>
									<p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
										Restore your setup in minutes from a USB drive or private Git repo. Safely share a local server using a tunneling service.
									</p>
								</div>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
